{"tid":509270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple玩完！A股概念股大跌 至停版！鄭州廠緊急暫停招工","createTime":"2017-12-25T06:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T11:47:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"596a055146d232e9909e2e21a2710a762e7fdc8c","tid":509270,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"新浪財經訊 12月25日消息，剛過完&ldquo;黑五&rdquo;銷售旺季又迎聖誕假日之際，iPhone X再度傳出負面消息，蘋果產業鏈相關個股周一均紛紛下挫，截止發稿，科森科技(27.530, -1.37, -4.74%)<span style=\"color: red;\">跌停</span>，報26.01元，藍思科技(28.590, -2.46, -7.92%)、安潔科技(25.810, -2.69, -9.44%)、創聯電子跌幅均超7%，共達電聲(8.440, -0.37, -4.20%)、超聲電子(13.480, -1.01, -6.97%)、歌爾股份(16.880, -0.66, -3.76%)等相關概念股均紛紛下挫。<br />\n<br />\n　　消息面：<br />\n<br />\n　　耶誕節當天，台灣經濟 日報援引供應鏈消息稱，iPhone X銷售不如預期，蘋果下修明年首季銷量預估，從原訂單季5000萬部大減四成，至3000萬部，減幅超乎市場此前的預期。<br />\n<br />\n　　報導還稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">獨家組裝iPhone X的鴻海富士康旗下鄭州工廠緊急宣佈，自12月25日起全面暫停招工</span>，沒有出現之前生產旺季時的連續加速招工現象。<br />\n<br />\n　　本月中旬，市場傳出蘋果公司對代工廠原本的追單反轉為砍單，公司大砍針對台積電的A11處理器訂單，明年第一季度A11的投片量比本季銳減三成。有分析推斷，iPhoneX明年第一季度訂單量也會隨之下調30%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/gujiayidong/2017-12-25/doc-ifypxrpp3790984.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fstock%2Fgujiayidong%2F2017-12-25%2Fdoc-ifypxrpp3790984.shtml&d=tChkqxY43xZa1fhjETCzmgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6a944468\" target=\"_blank\">http://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/gujiayidong/2017-12-25/doc-ifypxrpp3790984.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"27db3ddf1533c3d098b785a6d88a13dd00a7619f","tid":509270,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640a3036d9d0f886fa1aa088c99c73f5c